{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "本章回目\"生死两渺茫\"。云铮奉少林无色大师之命觐见常春岛日后娘娘，转达调停武林公案之意，遭日后娘娘严词拒绝。云铮恢复大旗弟子身份，为救温黛黛与日后激烈对峙。日后娘娘以温黛黛不能嫁大旗门下为由逼迫二人分离，温黛黛陷入两难。云铮悲愤之下扑攻日后被击退，日后暗示他唯有以死才能让温黛黛解脱，云铮毅然投身万丈绝壑。日后娘娘转身时泪流满面，透露其内心并非无情。与此同时，阴仪、阴嫔、易冰梅、冷青萍在海边与失散三十年的大姐阴素重逢。阴嫔讲述阴素当年救下大旗门弟子云九霄并深爱他的往事，以及阴素七次追赴塞外均被赶回的悲惨经历。冷青萍透露自己大姐也被大旗门五马分尸的相似悲剧。阴素揭示大旗门代代相传的无情传统，以及掌门自己也曾将爱人推落绝壁的隐秘。冷青萍得知铁中棠已死的消息后晕厥。然而铁中棠实未死，正藏身于海边山岩礁石之后。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "大旗弟子参见日后娘娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你是奉谁之命来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "弟子乃是奉少林无色大师之命前来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你既奉无色大师之命前来，便该以少林弟子身份觐见，知道么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "无色大师令你前来，是为何事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "无色大师令弟子转禀娘娘，说是江湖动乱已久，也该让武林朋友稍得安歇，那件纠缠数十年，几乎将天下武林高手，全都牵涉在其中的公案，此时也该作一了结，望娘娘上体苍天好生之德，下体无辜遭劫之苦，更该念此一公案中人，俱已被积年仇杀，逼得流离颠沛，苦不堪言，有时连亲人尸首都难收葬，惩罚也该够了，是以但请娘娘得放手时且放手，早些将此公案……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "住口！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你也想教训我么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "这番话全属无色大师所言，弟子只是将之一字不漏，转禀娘娘，至于所说的为何公案，弟子毫不知情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "无色也未免将自己看得过高了，凭什么他来管这闲事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "他要你前来，只是说这几句话么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "就是这些话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你不妨回去告诉他，此事既非我种因，亦非我能了结，我一向只是袖手不问，此后还是袖手不问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "无色若想将此公案了结，不妨自己设法，莫再寻着我。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "谁答应你带她走的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你方才明明说不留她，此刻又不放她，莫非是故意消遣于我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "她无论要去何处，我都不会留她，但要和你同走，却是万万不可。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "她若要寻个归宿，纵是嫁于市井无赖，贩夫走卒，俱无不可，却万万不能嫁给大旗门下。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "只因大旗门男子，俱是无情无义的畜生。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "放……谁说的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你此刻若是要走，我也不留你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "娘娘，我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "但你临走之前，却要发下重誓，今生今世，决不和'大旗门'弟子交谈一言半语。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你不能么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我……我留在这里。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你若要留在这里，也得发下重誓，从今而后，永不再对'大旗'弟子有所思念。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我不能不想他，我实在不能不想他。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "常春岛上，俱是心如止水之人，你若要想他，便不能待在这常春岛上。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "娘娘，你怎么能令人做不能做到的事，你……你不如让我死吧！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "看来你只有死了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你也敢无礼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "凭你这样的武功若想救她性命，除非一死。你若死了，她才可定下心来，只看你有没有决心死的勇气？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "原来你只是要我死么？那还不容易，云某早已活得不耐烦了。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "温黛黛，我生不能陪着你，死后却再也无人能阻我与你相见了。二哥，你也慢走一步……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将温黛黛送入留云馆，好生看着她。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "日后娘娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想大旗门下，竟终于有了个为情而死的男子……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "大姐……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "三妹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "大姐，真……真的是你？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "不是我是谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "阴仪",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "大姐，真的是你……大姐，真的是你……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "text": "二妹……二妹……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "阴仪",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "三十年不见，不想终是还能见着大姐一面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "text": "三十年……三十年了，唉！日子过得有时是那么慢，但有时又觉得三十年只是一转眼的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "text": "你可忘了么？我临走的时候，还替你们梳了次头发，想不到……现在……你头发都白了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "阴仪",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "大姐头发也白了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "text": "白了白了！二十年前就白了，唉……想不到一转眼间，我竟已有三十年未替你梳头。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "text": "你还记得么？这梳子就是昔日我为你梳头的那把。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "阴仪",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "记得。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "text": "你瞧你的头发又乱了，过来……让我再替你梳次头。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天可怜见，天可怜见，让我阴氏三姐妹，终又回到一处。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "阴仪",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "可笑我第一次坐上大姐这艘船，竟不认得大姐了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "可不是么，若不是我坚持着再回来瞧瞧，大姐只怕已气得不理我们了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大姐怎会怪你们？我若不说，你们又怎会想到这船上的可怜老太婆，便是昔日的异人阴素？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们坐着，大姐去替你们倒碗糖水吃。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "大姐还真的把我们当小孩子么？我们现在只喝酒，不吃糖水了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "你们不吃，那边两个小孩儿总要吃的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "text": "说真的，这三十年来，大姐你究竟到哪儿去了，大旗门那姓云的……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "无妨，让她说吧，近年来，我早已麻木了，往事早已不能再折磨我了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "那姓云的可死了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "他还好好的活着。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个没良心的，竟抛下姐姐一个人在这里，若不是姐姐救他，他还能活到现在？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "你们两个小丫头，可是想听听这段故事？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说给你们听听也好，好教你们日后小心些，莫要上了那些臭男人的当。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时我年纪还小，我们三姐妹，住在一栋有着大花园的房子。花园很大，种满各种鲜花，四时不断……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时的日子过得真妙，我们姐妹练完了武功，就在花园里修花、剪草、捉蜻蜓、扑蝴蝶，但是……有一天，花园里突然闯入个满身鲜血的人，他受的伤极重，一进花园，就扑地昏倒了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们三姐妹跑过去，只见这男人虽然满身鲜血，显得有些怕人，但模样生得可是真俊。尤其是，他脸色苍白得不带一丝血色，更显得有一种说不出的魅力，看了真教人心动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但那时我不过只觉他生得很俊而已，却不知我大姐仅只瞧了他一眼，就已……就已偷偷爱上了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们瞧他神色，就知道他必定乃是被极厉害的仇家追赶，惊惶之中，才会闯入我们的花园。二姐那时就似乎已猜着了大姐的心意，故意说：'此人又不知是什么来历，我们何必为他惹麻烦？不如送他走吧！'大姐心里虽不愿，但到底年轻面薄，也不好怎么说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在那时，墙外已响起呼喝叱咤之声，显然是追兵已来了，而且追来的人人数还不少。大姐虽未说话，却突然抱起那男人，将他藏了起来，然后行所无事地修花剪草，竟不瞧我和二姐一眼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追兵终于追进了花园，大姐非但没有说出那男人的事，反而说他们擅闯私宅，将他们痛骂了一顿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从那天之后，大姐花也不修了，草也不剪了，整天去服侍那男人，替他治伤，弄出各式各样好东西给他吃。过了一个多月，那男人伤势总算好了，大姐整日守候在病榻旁，日久情生，更是对他着了迷，哪知……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "哪知怎样？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪知那男人伤好了之后，竟悄悄走了，只留下张字条，说是要大姐永远忘记他。但大姐怎么忘得了他？大姐知道我们反对，竟说也不跟我们说一声，就悄悄地追了去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "后来怎样？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "后来我也不知道了，我也要问大姐。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后来我终于追着了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那一段日子，我们过得真是美，我们从早到晚，整天在一起，就连他都似乎将一切事都忘记了。但是……但是有些事却是忘不了的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们门户为了复仇，要远赴塞外，而他们门户的规矩，是绝对不许带女子同行的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "就是妻子也不行么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "text": "妻子也不行。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "易冰梅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好狠，好狠。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们离别了妻子，为的只是不愿练武时分神，更不愿他们下一代受到丝毫母爱。他们在冰天雪地里训练自己，训练他们的儿女，训练的严格与残忍，真是教人看了动心。他们要将儿女训练成铁一般身子，还要将儿女训练成铁一般心肠，若是母亲在那里，就不会狠下这个心来。只因我后来不顾一切，还是追到塞外，所以看到了这些，我虽然心狠，却也不禁看得流泪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "大姐竟追到塞外去了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一生去了七次，每一次都被他们掌门人赶了回来。只因我总是不死心，无论吃多么大的苦，受多么大罪，有时甚至被打得遍体都是伤，但只要我伤一好，我还是追了去。他们食粮本少，有好的都给了孩子吃，要孩子长得快，我在冰天雪地里追他们，更是寻不着吃的。有时我一饿就是一两天，饿得连藏在雪地里的老鼠、毒蛇，都被我挠了出来，用火烤了吃。我求他们只要让我跟着，什么苦我都愿意。我用尽了各种法子，说尽了各种好话，甚至……甚至下跪。但……但他们还……还是不动心，还是要赶我……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难……难怪大姐你……你如今竟变得……变得如此苍老了……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_mu_yin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "阴仪",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "大姐你既是受了这么多苦，就该一直追到底，除非……除非他们真把你杀了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "你就从此不追了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大姐你真是，那姓云的既然忍心见你受苦，不管你，你又何必再管他的生死。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "他……他也没法子，除非他竟敢背叛门户。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "speaker_name": "冷青萍",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "那姓云的……的老前辈，是否'铁血大旗门'的弟子？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "text": "你……你怎会知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "speaker_name": "冷青萍",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "我……我大姐的遭遇，也……也和老前辈的完全一样，只怕还……还要惨些。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "text": "真……真的？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "speaker_name": "冷青萍",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "我大姐也是在堡中救了个姓云的大旗弟子，也是悄悄爱上了他，而且还为他生了个孩子……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "text": "后来怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "speaker_name": "冷青萍",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "后……后来此事被'大旗门'的掌门人知道，我姐夫就……就被他们五马分尸了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "speaker_name": "冷青萍",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "那大旗掌门，就是我姐夫的亲生爹爹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那大旗掌门，真是个没有心肝的人，我若见了他，定要把他胸膛剖开瞧瞧他的心是什么做的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的遭遇，昔日本也一样，他也爱上了个女人，这女子却和他仇家有些关系……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事自也被他爹爹知道，但他却真狠得下心，将那女子活生生推落绝壁之下。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "speaker_name": "冷青萍",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "你……你那……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "text": "我丈夫云九霄，就是他亲生弟弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_qing_ping",
      "speaker_name": "冷青萍",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "他……他既然自己也受过这样的苦，为什么还要对他亲生的弟弟和儿子如此狠心？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 547
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是'铁血大旗'无情的传统。他们代代相传，都是如此，而且……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且据说'大旗门'每一代弟子，都有过我这样差不多的悲惨的事。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
      "speaker_name": "阴嫔",
      "listener": "char_yin_su",
      "text": "这些事我从来未曾听人提起，大姐你……你却又怎会知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 557
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": "char_yin_pin",
      "text": "我自然知道……想来你们日后自也会知道的，知道得比现在还多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_pin",
