      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_su",
      "speaker_name": "阴素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要送饭，你们也该走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "乌衫少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了，你们先让婆婆送饭去，回来再聊天，否则若是让人饿着了，可真不好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "乌衫少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们才来没多久，我们也正好闲着，吃过饭，让我们陪你们到各处看看好么？",
